{"tid":370722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門威尼斯人賭場水浸","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T22:09:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d1b9977bb8bbcd8332da6fc8ecb0e4c800968f","tid":370722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170823/s00001/8bed625ba6962ec3e85b2a93c88bf651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170823%2Fs00001%2F8bed625ba6962ec3e85b2a93c88bf651.jpg&h=22d76fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「天鴿」來襲，澳門廣泛地區受波及，出現停電、水浸。澳門北區及內港一帶嚴重水浸，全澳大停電。電力公司現時正搶修，逐步恢復電力，並呼籲市民節約用電。網上有照片顯示，威尼斯人酒店內的賭場水浸，路邊有貨車被吹翻，十六浦嚴重水浸，水位及腰。<br />\n<br />\n多張圖片及多段影片顯示，天鴿襲澳情況混亂。有路邊的貨車吹翻，十六浦嚴重水浸，水位高度逾一米到腰間。威尼斯人酒店內的賭場水浸。澳門筷子基有大樹倒塌，連根拔起，橫卧路面。<br />\n<br />\n《愛瞞日報》表示，不少市民倉促逃生，內港地舖商戶預料損失慘重，又引述市民批評當局明知風暴會正面而來，但延至今日上午9時才改掛8號風球，令不少人低估風暴威力，來不及做防洪措施。"},{"pid":"333b46285f16731bef622a7ae64de1894410e088","tid":370722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86681af99a23f8505805e2990f082c430a96796f","tid":370722,"uid":34503,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:41:30.000Z","msg":"賭場水浸好意頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f2c481ff5246cdd7d1a7158507c1dd7dd534ba","tid":370722,"uid":19557,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"真係威尼斯喇今鋪"},{"pid":"95f1d3be83d3a723f0089dafa9c89633e42a3d8d","tid":370722,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6735311c98fd225d72a5e2f58578e1c939ca21cf","tid":370722,"uid":50327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"咁廢既天文台係